        <header style="color: rgb(114, 114, 114);font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;" id="isPasted"><h1 style="font-size: 25px;margin: 0px 0px 25px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;">O&#39;zbekistonda ayollar orasidagi ishsizlik sabablari</h1></header><footer style="margin-bottom: 25px;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;"><span style="font-size: 14px;height: 21.0085px;margin-right: 15px;border-right: none;">&nbsp;<a href="https://ifmr.uz/ru/4823/" rel="bookmark" style="background-color: transparent;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);text-decoration: inherit;font-size: 12px;"><time datetime="2020-11-25T21:34:42+05:00">6 марта 2024</time></a></span></footer><p><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" width="400" height="267" src="https://imrs.uz/images/publications/ru/298921.png" alt="" style="margin-left:27%;border: 0px; height: auto; color: rgb(114, 114, 114); font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px;" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><div style="color: rgb(114, 114, 114);font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;"><div style="margin: 0px;"><div data-elementor-type="wp-post" data-elementor-id="4823" data-elementor-settings="[]"><section data-id="3a4a538" data-element_type="section" style=" border-box;display: block;position: relative;"><div style=" border-box;display: flex;margin-right: auto;margin-left: auto;position: relative;max-width: 100%;"><div style=" border-box;width: 1160px;display: flex;"><div data-id="b12e115" data-element_type="column" style=" border-box;position: relative;min-height: 1px;display: flex;width: 1160px;"><div style=" border-box;width: 1160px;position: relative;display: flex;padding: 0px 10px 10px;"><div style=" border-box;position: relative;width: 1140px;flex-wrap: wrap;align-content: flex-start;display: flex;"><div data-id="7c752be" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default" style=" border-box;position: relative;color: rgb(122, 122, 122);font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;width: 1140px;"><div style=" border-box;transition: background 0.3s ease 0s, border 0.3s ease 0s, border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-border-radius 0.3s ease 0s, -webkit-box-shadow 0.3s ease 0s;"><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;"><strong style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">2024-yilning&nbsp;</strong>boshida<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</b>O&lsquo;zbekiston aholisi<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</b><strong style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">36799 ming</strong> kishiga yetdi va&nbsp;<strong style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">2023-yilning</strong> mos davridagiga nisbatan&nbsp;<strong style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">2,2 foizga&nbsp;</strong>yoki<strong style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;775 ming&nbsp;</strong>kishiga oshdi. Aholi orasida ayolarning ulushi&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">49,7 foizni</b> tashkil etdi. O&lsquo;zbekistonda ayollar orasidagi ishsizlik darajasi so&lsquo;nggi paytlarda ortib borayapti. Ayollar orasidagi&nbsp;<i style=" border-box;font-style: italic;">yuqori ishsizlik ko&lsquo;rsatkichlari</i> va&nbsp;<i style=" border-box;font-style: italic;">past iqtisodiy faollik darajasi&nbsp;</i>bir tomondan yuqori tug&lsquo;ilish ko&lsquo;rsatkichlari va ayollarning uy ishlariga ko&lsquo;p vaqt ajratishi bilan bog&lsquo;liq bo&lsquo;lsa, ikkinchi tomondan aholi mentaliteti bilan ham bog&lsquo;liq. Xususan,<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;"><em style=" border-box;font-style: italic;">&nbsp;</em></b><b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">2023-yilda</b> respublikada&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">961 ming</b> nafar chaqaloq dunyoga kelgan. Bu esa o&lsquo;z navbatida ayollarning mehnat bozoridan vaqtincha bo&lsquo;lsada chiqib ketishi va iqtisodiy nofaol maqomiga tushishiga olib kelmoqda. Shuningdek, O&lsquo;zbekistonda ayollar vaqtining&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">22 foizini</b> uy yumushlari va bola parvarishiga sarflaydi (erkaklar&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">9 soat</b> vaqtini uy ishlariga sarflaydi).</span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-indent: 42.55pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;">Dunyoda ayollar orasidagi o&lsquo;rtacha ishsizlik darajasi&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">5,3 foizni</b> tashkil etadi. Bu ko&lsquo;rsatkich Qozog&lsquo;istonda&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">5,5</b> foizni, Rossiyada&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">4</b> foizni, Ozarbayjonda&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">6,5</b> foizni, Belarusda 2,8 foizni, Bangladeshda 6,5 foizni, Xitoyda 4,3 foizni tashkil etmoqda.&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">2022-yil</b> natijalariga ko&lsquo;ra, O&lsquo;zbekistonda ayollar orasidagi ishsizlik darajasi&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">13,4 foizni</b> tashkil etdi (ushbu ko&lsquo;rsatkich erkaklar orasida 5,4 foizga teng).<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;2018 - 2022</b> yillarda ayollar orasidagi ishsizlik darajasi&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">1,8 foiz</b> punktiga o&lsquo;sgan.<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;</b>Ayollar orasida ishsizlikning eng past ko&lsquo;rsatkichlari&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">Toshkent shahri</b> (7,9),&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">Namangan</b> (11,9) va&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">Toshkent&nbsp;</b>(12,8) viloyatlarida kuzatilmoqda.</span></h3><ol style=" border-box;margin: 0px 0px 0.5em;list-style: decimal;padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px;"><li align="right" style=" border-box;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: 164px;text-align: right;"><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 0px 0px 15px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:15px;"><span style=" border-box;line-height: 15.6933px;"><span style=" border-box;font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;"><span style=" border-box;line-height: 19.9733px;">Rasm</span></span></span></span></span></h3></li></ol><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: center;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:15px;"><span style=" border-box;line-height: 15.6933px;"><span style=" border-box;font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;"><span style=" border-box;line-height: 19.9733px;">2018-2022 yillarda ayollar va erkaklar orasidagi ishsizlik darajasi</span></span></strong></span></span></span></h3><p style=" border-box;margin: 0px 0px 15px;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);"><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" src="https://imrs.uz/public/ckfinder/userfiles/files/image(309).png" style="border: none; height: 334px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none; width: 950px;" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></p><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;">&nbsp;</h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:13px;">Manba: Statistika agentligi ma&rsquo;lumotlari</span></span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;text-indent: 42.55pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;">Ayollar orasidagi ishsizlik sabablarini aniqlash va ilmiy asoslangan chora-tadbirlar ishlab chiqish maqsadida&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">MHTI&nbsp;</b>mutaxassislari tomonidan ayollar orasida so&lsquo;rov o&lsquo;tkazildi.</span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;text-indent: 42.55pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;">So&lsquo;rovda&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">300 nafar</b> ayol ishtirok etdi. Ularning o&lsquo;rtacha yoshi&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">35 ga teng.</b> Respondentlarning deyarli&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">67 foizi</b> oilali,&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">72 foizi</b> oliy ma&rsquo;lumotli. So&lsquo;rovda qatnashgan ayollarning&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">58,9</b> foizi iqtisodiyotda band,&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">14,5 foizi</b> ishsiz,&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">25,5 foizi</b> uy bekasi yoki tug&lsquo;ruq ta&rsquo;tilida. So&lsquo;rovda qatnashgan ayollarning&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">22 foizi</b> bakalavr,&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">18 foizi</b> magistratura bosqichini davlat granti asosida tamomlagan.</span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;text-indent: 42.55pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;">Respondentlarning asosiy qismi&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">ta&rsquo;lim</b> (29 foiz),&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">sog&lsquo;liqni saqlash</b> (13 foiz) va&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">axborot texnologiyalari</b> (6,3 foiz) sohalarida band.</span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;text-indent: 42.55pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;"><span style=" border-box;background: white;">So&lsquo;rovda ishtirok etgan ishsiz respondentlarning o&lsquo;rtacha yoshi&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">32 ga teng.</b> Ularning&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">56 foizi oliy</b> (ular orasida bakalavr bosqichini davlat granti asosida tamomlaganlar 25,5 foiz, magistratura bosqichini tamomlaganlar 25,6 foiz),&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">29 foizi</b> o&lsquo;rta maxsus ma&rsquo;lumotga ega.</span></span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;text-indent: 42.55pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;"><span style=" border-box;background: white;">Ularning deyarli&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">54 foizi</b> 3 yildan oshiq vaqt mobaynida ishsiz.</span></span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;text-indent: 42.55pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;"><span style=" border-box;background: white;">So&lsquo;rovda ishtirok etgan ishsiz ayollarning ishlamaslik sabablari qilib:</span></span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;text-indent: 42.55pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;"><span style=" border-box;background: white;"><strong style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">8,5 foizi</strong> ishlash istagi yo&lsquo;qligi, &nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">7,5 foizi</b> turmush o&lsquo;rtog&lsquo;i ruxsat bermasligi,<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">&nbsp;19,5 foizi</b> uy ishlari va farzandlar tarbiyasidan ortmasligi,&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">22,7 foizi</b> ish o&lsquo;rinlarining yo&lsquo;qligi yoki ularda taklif etilayotgan oylik maoshlar pastligi,&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">5,3 foizi</b> ish o&lsquo;rinlari to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida ma&rsquo;lumotga ega emasligini bildirgan.</span></span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;text-indent: 42.55pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;"><span style=" border-box;background: white;">Shuningdek,&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">13,4 foizi</b> tanish bilishlarsiz ishga kirish qiyinligini, va&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">4,9</b> foizi birorta ko&lsquo;nikmaga ega emasligini bildirgan.</span></span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;text-indent: 42.55pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;"><span style=" border-box;background: white;">So&lsquo;rovda ishtirok etgan ishsiz ayollarning&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">85,4 foizi</b> ishlash istagi borligini bildirgan, lekin shunga qaramay ularning bor-yo&lsquo;g&lsquo;i&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">24,4 foizi</b> mehnat organlariga murojaat qilgan.</span></span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;text-indent: 42.55pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;"><span style=" border-box;background: white;">Respondentlarning deyarli&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">75 foizi</b> kasbiy ko&lsquo;nikmaga ega ekanligini bildirgan bo&lsquo;lishiga qaramay,&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">62 foizi</b> yangi kasb o&lsquo;rganish istagida ekanligi ma&rsquo;lum bo&lsquo;ldi.&nbsp;</span></span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;text-indent: 42.55pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;"><span style=" border-box;background: white;">So&lsquo;rovda ishtirok etgan ishsiz ayollarning asosiy qismi (<strong style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">40 foizi</strong>)&nbsp;<i style=" border-box;font-style: italic;">sog&lsquo;liqni saqlash</i> va&nbsp;<i style=" border-box;font-style: italic;">ta&rsquo;lim</i> tizimida mehnat qilish istagi borligini bildirgan.</span></span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;text-indent: 42.55pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;">So&lsquo;rovda ishtirok etgan ayollarning&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">55 foizi</b> tadbirkorlik faoliyati bilan shug&lsquo;ullanish istagi borligini ta&rsquo;kidlagan.</span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;text-indent: 42.55pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;"><em style=" border-box;font-style: italic;">Bugungi kunda ayollar biznesini tashkil qilishga qanday omillar qiyinchilik tug&lsquo;diradi</em> deb hisoblaysiz, degan savolga respondentlarning&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">45 foizi</b> <i style=" border-box;font-style: italic;">mablag&lsquo;</i>,&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">24 foizi</b> <i style=" border-box;font-style: italic;">bilim&nbsp;</i>va<i style=" border-box;font-style: italic;">&nbsp;ko&lsquo;nikma</i>,&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">15 foizi</b> <i style=" border-box;font-style: italic;">garov mulki</i> yetishmasligini bildirgan bo&lsquo;lsa,&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">13,5 foizi</b> <i style=" border-box;font-style: italic;">kredit olishdagi</i> qiyinchiliklar,&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">22 foizi</b> <i style=" border-box;font-style: italic;">farzand tarbiyasi va uy ishlaridan</i> ortmayotganini aytgan.</span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;text-indent: 42.55pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;">Respondentlarning fikriga ko&lsquo;ra,&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">ayollarni ish bilan ta&rsquo;minlash uchun quyidagi masalalarga e&rsquo;tibor qaratish zarur:</b></span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;text-indent: 42.55pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;">- &nbsp;kasbga qayta tayyorlash va o&lsquo;qitish tizimini takomillashtirish va kengaytirish (<strong style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">50</strong> foiz);</span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;text-indent: 42.55pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;">- mehnat bozori to&lsquo;g&lsquo;risida muntazam ravishda ma&rsquo;lumotlar berib borish (<strong style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">39</strong> foiz);</span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;text-indent: 42.55pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;">- ayollar biznesi uchun bino va inshootlarni bepul ijaraga berishni rivojlantirish (<strong style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">34,8</strong> foiz);</span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;text-indent: 42.55pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;">- maktabgacha ta&rsquo;lim tizimi qamrovini kengaytirish (<strong style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">31,5</strong> foiz);</span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;text-indent: 42.55pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;">- mehnat yarmarkalari ko&lsquo;lamini kengaytirish (<strong style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">32,2</strong> foiz);</span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;text-indent: 42.55pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;">- mehnat migratsiyasini rivojlantirish (<strong style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">8,7</strong> foiz). &nbsp;</span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;text-indent: 42.55pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;">So&lsquo;rov ma&rsquo;lumotlaridan foydalangan xolda&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">MHTI ekspertlari</b> ayollarning ishlash va ishlamaslik ehtimoliga ta&rsquo;sir etuvchi omillarni ekonometrik jihatdan tahlil qildi. Tahlilda logit va probit modellaridan foydalanildi. Natijalarga ko&lsquo;ra, so&lsquo;rovda ishtirok etgan ayollarning ishlash yoki ishlamasligiga ularning oilaviy holati, ta&rsquo;lim darajasi va yoshi ta&rsquo;sir qilishi aniqlandi. Model natijalari&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">1-jadvalda</b> keltirilgan.</span></h3><ol style=" border-box;margin: 0px 0px 0.5em;list-style: decimal;padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px;"><li align="right" style=" border-box;margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;margin-left: 504px;text-align: right;"><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 0px 0px 15px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:15px;"><span style=" border-box;line-height: 15.6933px;"><span style=" border-box;font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;"><span style=" border-box;line-height: 19.9733px;">jadval</span></span></span></span></span></h3></li></ol><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: center;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:15px;"><span style=" border-box;line-height: 15.6933px;"><span style=" border-box;font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;"><span style=" border-box;line-height: 19.9733px;">Ayollarning ishlash yoki ishlamasligiga ta&rsquo;sir etuvchi omillarning ekonometrik tahlili</span></span></strong></span></span></span></h3><table width="760" style=" border-box;border-collapse: collapse;border-spacing: 0px;margin: 0px 0px 1.5em;width: 608px;border: none;"><tbody><tr><td valign="top" style=" border-box;padding: 0cm 7px;border-top: none;border-right: none;border-bottom: 1px solid black;border-left: none;border-image: initial;width: 371px;height: 40px;backg