ight: 42px;vertical-align: top;"><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: right;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;"><span style=" border-box;line-height: 21.4667px;"><strong style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;"><span style=" border-box;line-height: 21.4667px;">0,000</span></strong></span></span></h3></td></tr><tr><td valign="top" style=" border-box;padding: 0cm 7px;border: none;width: 371px;height: 40px;vertical-align: top;"><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;"><span style=" border-box;line-height: 21.4667px;"><span style=" border-box;line-height: 21.4667px;">Kuzatuvlar soni</span></span></span></h3></td><td colspan="2" valign="top" style=" border-box;padding: 0cm 7px;border: none;width: 389px;height: 40px;vertical-align: top;"><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: center;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;"><span style=" border-box;line-height: 21.4667px;"><strong style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong><b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;"><span style=" border-box;line-height: 21.4667px;">319</span></b></span></span></h3></td></tr></tbody></table><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=" border-box;font-size:13px;">Manba: MHTI hisob-kitoblari</span></span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;text-indent: 35.4pt;">&nbsp;</h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-indent: 35.4pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;">Ekonometrik tahlil natijalariga ko&lsquo;ra, ayollarning oliy ma&rsquo;lumotga ega bo&lsquo;lishi ularning ishlash ehtimolini&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">0,99</b> foizga oshiradi, oilali bo&lsquo;lish esa ishlash ehtimolini&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">1,35</b> foizga kamaytiradi, ayol yoshining kattalashishi uning ishlash ehtimolini&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">0,08</b> foizga oshiradi.</span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-indent: 35.4pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;">Bundan tashqari, Statistika agentligi ma&rsquo;lumotlari asosida tayyorlangan korrelyatsion bog&lsquo;liqlik natijasiga ko&lsquo;ra, ayollar orasidagi ishsizlikka eng avvolo tug&lsquo;ilishlar va nikohlar soni ta&rsquo;sir etishi ma&rsquo;lum bo&lsquo;ldi. Ishsiz ayollar va tug&lsquo;ilishlar orasidagi korrelyatsion bog&lsquo;liqlik koeffitsienti&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">0,79 ga</b> teng bo&lsquo;lsa, nikohlar bilan bog&lsquo;liqlik&nbsp;<b style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">0,73&nbsp;</b>ga teng ekanligi aniqlandi. Tug&lsquo;ilishlar bilan bog&lsquo;liqlikning mavjudligi bu tabiiy xol, lekin O&lsquo;zbekiston sharoitida ayollar turmush qurib ham ishsiz bo&lsquo;lishining kuzatilishi, avvalo aholi orasidagi mental qarashlarga borib taqaladi. 2-rasmda ayollar ishsizligi tug&lsquo;ilishlar soni va tuzilayotgan nikohlar o&lsquo;rtasidagi bog&lsquo;liqlikni ko&lsquo;rish mumkin.</span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: right;text-indent: 35.4pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;">2-rasm</span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: center;text-indent: 35.4pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;"><strong style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">Ayollar orasidagi ishsizlik, tug&lsquo;ilishlar va nikohlar o&lsquo;rtasidagi bog&lsquo;liqlik</strong></span></h3><p style=" border-box;margin: 0px 0px 15px;color: rgb(114, 114, 114);">&nbsp;</p><table style=" border-box;border-collapse: collapse;border-spacing: 0px;margin: 0px 0px 1.5em;width: 1140px;border: none;"><tbody><tr><td valign="top" style=" border-box;padding: 0cm 7px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);width: 389px;height: 302px;vertical-align: top;"><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: center;"><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" src="https://imrs.uz/public/ckfinder/userfiles/files/image(310).png" style="border: none; height: 427px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none; width: 486px;" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></h3></td><td valign="top" style=" border-box;padding: 0cm 7px;border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);width: 389px;height: 302px;vertical-align: top;"><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: center;"><img data-fr-image-pasted="true" src="https://imrs.uz/public/ckfinder/userfiles/files/image(311).png" style="border: none; height: 425px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 0px; box-shadow: none; width: 472px;" class="fr-fic fr-dii"></h3></td></tr></tbody></table><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;text-indent: 35.4pt;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;"><strong style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;">So&lsquo;rov natijalari va ekonometrik hisob-kitoblardan kelib chiqib, ayollar orasidagi ishsizlikni kamaytirish uchun quyidagilar taklif etiladi:</strong></span></h3><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:15px;"><span style=" border-box;line-height: normal;"><span style=" border-box;font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><strong style=" border-box;font-weight: 700;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;"><span style=" border-box;letter-spacing: -0.4pt;">Ayollar ta&rsquo;limini rivojlantirish:</span></span></strong></span></span></span></h3><ul style=" border-box;margin: 0px 0px 0.5em;list-style: disc;padding: 0px 0px 0px 20px;"><li><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:15px;"><span style=" border-box;line-height: normal;"><span style=" border-box;font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:19px;"><span style=" border-box;letter-spacing: -0.4pt;">xususiy o&lsquo;quv markazlarida (Prezident maktablariga tayyorlov kurslari, ingliz tilini o&lsquo;rgatish kurslari va h.k.)qizlarini o&lsquo;qitayotgan ota-onalar uchun kurs to&lsquo;lovi badalini daromad solig&lsquo;i hisobidan qaytarish tizimini joriy etish;</span></span></span></span></span></h3></li><li><h3 style=" border-box;margin: 8px 0px;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;font-family: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;font-weight: 400;font-size: 20px;clear: both;text-align: justify;"><span style=" border-box;font-size:15px;"><span style=" border-box